OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1779909062
OL,3,CNine arrested and 250 turned away in
OL,4,Cdispersal order crackdown
OL,6,FNine people have been arrested and 250
OL,7,Fturned away at railway stations as
OL,8,FEssex Police tackle disorder in
OL,9,FSouthend.
OL,11,FA dispersal order will be in force for
OL,12,Fmuch of the Southend district until
OL,13,F9:30am Thursday 28 May to help prevent
OL,14,Fdisorder or violent behaviour across
OL,15,Fthe city following an increased number
OL,16,Fof visitors.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
