OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1779909062
OL,3,CNine arrested and 250 turned away in
OL,4,Cdispersal order crackdown
OL,6,FIn a statement, Essex Police said: "A
OL,7,Fdispersal order is currently in place
OL,8,Facross much of the district and we are
OL,9,Fworking closely with our partners to
OL,10,Fdisrupt anybody travelling here to
OL,11,Fcommit crime.
OL,13,F"They will be dealt with robustly to
OL,14,Fensure everyone is safe and can carry
OL,15,Fon with their plans.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
