FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1779909062
OL,3,CNine arrested and 250 turned away in
OL,4,Cdispersal order crackdown
OL,6,F"As part of this significant policing
OL,7,Foperation we have deployed a large
OL,8,Famount of additional officers in
OL,9,FSouthend ` they are here in response
OL,10,Fto information and vital intelligence
OL,11,Freceived from members of the public.
OL,13,FThey are working with the British
OL,14,FTransport Police and the council's
OL,15,FCCTV operators to track down and
OL,16,Farrest anyone committing criminal
OL,17,Foffences.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
