PN,41704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1779909062
OL,3,CNine arrested and 250 turned away in
OL,4,Cdispersal order crackdown
OL,6,F"Using our dispersal order powers we
OL,7,Fhave already turned 250 people away at
OL,8,Fthe railway stations and used our
OL,9,Fsection 60/60AA search powers to stop
OL,10,Fand search 29 people.
OL,12,F"We have made nine arrests, including
OL,13,Fone for possession of a bladed
OL,14,Farticle, and others thanks to the
OL,15,Fdeployment of our Live Facial
OL,16,FRecognition (LFR) technology."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
