CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1779909062
OL,3,CNine arrested and 250 turned away in
OL,4,Cdispersal order crackdown
OL,6,FThe area covered by the order, shown
OL,7,Fon the map, includes all of the
OL,8,FSouthend district south of the A13, as
OL,9,Fwell as several areas in the city
OL,10,Fcentre north of the A13.
OL,12,FThis area includes the Leigh-on-Sea,
OL,13,FChalkwell, Westcliff, Southend
OL,14,FCentral, Southend East, Thorpe Bay,
OL,15,FShoeburyness, Prittlewell and Southend
OL,16,FVictoria train stations, including
OL,17,Ftheir platforms, concourses, ticket
OL,18,Fhalls, forecourts and exits.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
