OL,3,CNine arrested and 250 turned away in
OL,4,Cdispersal order crackdown
OL,6,FPolice say they expect the vast
OL,7,Fmajority of people to enjoy the
OL,8,Fseafront responsibly, but that those
OL,9,Fwho do not should expect to be
OL,10,Fidentified, stopped and, where
OL,11,Fappropriate, arrested.
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
